data.description: Amazing Custom home with many upgrades. Home is on a large lot, at the end of a private drive with a 781 SQ FT guest house. The main house is 1867 Sq Ft. with coffered ceilings, extra storage including large linen closets, and a 200 Sq Ft. Bonus Room. Open Kitchen with Custom cabinets, granite counter tops w/bar seating, hardwood floors. Primary Suite w/large closets & gorgeous bath. High end touches throughout & lots of natural light. Retractable covered patio, Trex decking, large RV Pad, Raised Garden & Flower Beds, 2 shops, 1 insulated & wired, solar panels. Excludes Washer & Dryer, Sunroom Closets & Drawers. Guest house has large bedroom, nice kitchen & Laundry. Washer & Dryer in Guest house included. Please give seller a 1-hour notice
